00:40:25.900 --> 00:40:33.040
of -- there is one way in which you can query
that figure -- I don't think I'll get too

00:40:33.040 --> 00:40:36.890
technical on that.
Basically some of the very conservative, religious

00:40:36.890 --> 00:40:40.840
colleges aren't necessarily of the same caliber
