to get things through.

00:48:55.359 --> 00:49:01.350
They're very, very quick on to things like
_________ all those things.

00:49:01.350 --> 00:49:04.440
So it's pretty technophile.
Against that, you're right.

00:49:04.440 --> 00:49:09.410
There are some elements which are inherently
suspicious of it.

00:49:09.410 --> 00:49:13.760
The bit where they get into trouble has more
to do with biology than information technology,

00:49:13.760 --> 00:49:16.190
I think.
It's quite interesting actually, but in Africa,

00:49:16.190 --> 00:49:21.359
you can argue out of all the dominant religions
there -- and religions grow very quickly in

00:49:21.359 --> 00:49:27.109
Africa -- the only religion that now accepts
evolution, the big one is Catholicism, which

00:49:27.109 --> 00:49:41.119
is an interesting switch from where it was
around the time of Galileo.

